metadata.name: Miner Number Eleven/In The Lake
metadata.description:
The smell of spring pervades the region. At the end of the Sysphos's valley, miner number eleven witnessed another miner being killed by a snake. Now the water is safe, so she can dig in the lake.
She is a nun who left the monastery because one of the padres wanted to rape her. But she killed him. and escaped to the region. In the beginning, she tried to build a church, But she did not have this permission in the area. Because she was safe in the region, she stayed there. she is thirty-five years old and her name is Teresa.
(this is not just an image, this is part of the idea behind a video game and this is just the beginning)
